{"tid":1511852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對唔閪住 得罪啲講句 你家下同我講良知你仲有無良知","createTime":"2019-08-27T16:07:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T16:23:41.000Z","uid":292807,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e054508b1d429b54b53db4fba650a86393f59e45","tid":1511852,"uid":292807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T16:07:36.000Z","msg":"事源呢個post同一眾連登仔女講良知<br />\n<br />\n如果你真係選擇欺凌班警嘅細路 得罪講句你冇良知<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1511676\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1511676</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我想講 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">對住無良知嘅人係唔撚洗有良知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n我相信好多手足身邊都有人屋企冚家都係警察但都出嚟做前線嘅人，<span style=\"color: red;\">其實你問心無愧，其它人係有眼睇架</span>，你估真係個撚個都會被欺凌咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講真，比人欺凌嗰啲一撚定係有問題架啦，就算唔係撐警都一定係中立良知撚。<span style=\"color: red;\">真正既手足，係已經抱撚住一齊被清算嘅決心架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n如果有人再講良知的話<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">希望你屋企人被斬或者個女被人強姦嗰時，再同講番良知啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 禍必及妻兒<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />警蓄仔女是無辜的"},{"pid":"724647400dcfd78ab3e53b9b1127105e47760fbe","tid":1511852,"uid":55128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T16:07:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/suRKmvs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuRKmvs.gif&